Name: Open forum

Brief description: Each user will be able to open a forum for a specific purpose of his choice, whether it is a forum for talking about politics, the unit, jobs and so on...

players: user, admin, DB

preconditions:Log in successfully 

Basic flow:
	1)Click on menu
	2)Click on forums
	3)Click on open forum 
	4)Write a title and description for the forum and click on Post

alternate flow:----

exception flow:If the forum is not given a name and description, the app will mark the missing information in red and require the user to complete it


post conditions:The forum is given a name and description
